              a(target='_blank', href='https://jmorp.megabank.tohoku.ac.jp/202001/help/conditions-of-use')
                | https://jmorp.megabank.tohoku.ac.jp/202001/help/conditions-of-use
            li
              | PubTatorCentral:
              |
              a(target='_blank', href='ftp://ftp.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pub/lu/PubTatorCentral/README.txt')
                | ftp://ftp.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pub/lu/PubTatorCentral/README.txt
            li
              | JGA-NGS dataset:
              |
              a(href='/doc/ja/datasets/jga_ngs') https://togovar.biosciencedbc.jp/doc/ja/datasets/jga_ngs
            li
              | JGA-SNP dataset:
